Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,MARLIN. Maritime Anomaly and Risk Intelligence Layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM contested logistics: dark vessels and gray-zone rendezvous in\Nthe second island chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten vessel tracks. One thousand AIS pings. One hundred-event timeline\Nreplaying live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Three anomalies surface automatically: AIS gap, denied-area loiter,\Nand a midnight rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We click the flagged tanker. A Kamiwaza-deployed model reads the\Ntrack, neighbors, and denied areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A three-paragraph intel narrative streams in, citing specific\Ntimestamps and lat lon coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern of life. Anomaly analysis. A time-bounded recommendation for\Nthe watch officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A second JSON-mode call returns structured indicators ready for\Ntipping and cueing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Running on a Kamiwaza-deployed model behind KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL.\NAir-gapped, IL5/IL6 ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred percent data containment. Nothing leaves your accredited\Nenvironment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,MARLIN. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
